casebody.data:
William Friedman, Respondent, v. D. L. & D. Corrugated Paper Products Co., Inc., et al., Appellants.

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements, with leave to the defendants to answer within ten days after service of the order, with notice of entry thereof, on payment of said costs. No opinion. Present — Peck, P. J., Glennon, Cohn, Callahan and Shientag, JJ.
